headline: Keysight EDA and Intel Foundry Collaborate on EMIB-T Silicon Bridge Technology for Next-Generation AI and Data Center Solutions
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., April 29, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) announced today a collaboration with Intel Foundry to support Embedded Multi-die Interconnect Bridge-T (EMIB-T) technology, a cutting-edge innovation aimed at improving high-performance packaging solutions for artificial intelligence (AI) and data center markets in addition to the support of Intel 18A process node.
